                  and yet he beleeves that true love caſteth out fear.

135. He is no fighter;
1 Tim 6.12 
                  and yet alwayes fighting, (the good fight of faith.)

144. He beleeves that he is a cleanſed from all unrighteouſneſſe;
1 Joh. 1.9 
                  and yet he beleeves that all unrighteouſneſſe is not (clean) cleanſed from him.

